#ansible-playbook error

#실행 명령어
-ansible-playbook  ansible-nginx.yaml  -k

#error log
SSH password:
ERROR! couldn't resolve module/action 'firewalld'. This often indicates a misspelling, missing collection, or incorrect module path.

The error appears to be in '/root/ansible-nginx.yaml': line 22, column 7, but may
be elsewhere in the file depending on the exact syntax problem.

The offending line appears to be:


    - name: nginx-firewall-open
      ^ here


#문제 발생 이유

#Collection은 특정 기능만 배포하지만 포함되지 않은 기능은 실행 불가능
#Firewalld 기능이 ansible-core에 포함되지 않은 상태

#해결 방법

#Posix 다운로드

-ansible-galaxy collection install ansible.posix
#설치 확인
-ansible-galaxy collection list | grep posix
ansible.posix 2.1.0


